  "texts": [
    "Problem 8.9.",
    "Investigate degrees of K-incompleteness (Kripke-incompleteness) relative to FP as in § 7.1.Problem 8.10.",
    "Give a syntactic or alternative semantic characterization of the logics in ML(FP), or of the logics in the difference ML(FP) \\ ML(K).A direction that may lead to a better understanding of FP, mentioned at the end of § 7.4, is the following.",
    "Problem 8.11.",
    "Investigate notions of persistence of modal formulas from possibility frames to their associated full possibility frames.The same kinds of questions as in Problems 8.8-8.10 arise from the other strict inclusions above."
  ]
